nodes.text: Triewahl Docking Station was a space station in the Triewahl system.
It was where Callandri attempted to kill Alton Lochner after her first failure.

Callandri had been defeated by the combined might of Lochner's allies, including the Wookiee Tirranna and Adazian Liebke; thus, she associated with her cousin, Zayl Braith, and finally found Lochner on Triewahl.
However, Lochner survived this second attack, again thanks to Tirranna.
